      "content": "i understand what u mean about the doctor, but everything is so expensive and the blood tests cost a fortune. if i was just going to take a huge amount of garlic extract and lots of spinach smoothies every single day, how much do u think i'd need to take to actually see a real effect? like if i wanted to test it out and see if i could taper off the warfarin myself over a month or two, what kind of daily garlic dosage would be a good starting point to make sure it's actually working?",
